{"type":"message","id":"3b49bcea","parentId":"ad1f0f90","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:14:49.496Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Fallback** 是备用模型的意思。\n\n当主模型（Primary）不可用时，系统会自动切换到 Fallback 模型。\n\n**当前配置：**\n- **Primary:** `moonshot/kimi-k2.5` — 主要使用的模型\n- **Fallback:** `deepseek/deepseek-chat` — 当 Kimi 不可用时自动切换\n\n例如：\n- 如果 Moonshot API 服务中断或返回错误\n- 如果 API key 失效\n- 如果请求超时\n\n系统会自动使用 DeepSeek 作为备用。\n\n---\n\n您想要调整这个配置吗？比如：\n1. **交换主次** — 让 DeepSeek 作为主模型，Kimi 作为备用\n2. **移除 Fallback** — 只使用一个模型\n3. **添加更多 Fallback** — 多个备用层级"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":317,"output":170,"cacheRead":69632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70119,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773742483262}}
