laude, including the current (most recent)   |                    |\n|           |                                     | model or a full model breakdown. Trigger      |                    |\n|           |                                     | when asked for model-level usage/cost data    |                    |\n|           |                                     | from codexbar, or when you need a scriptable  |                    |\n|           |                                     | per-model summary from codexbar cost JSON.    |                    |\n| ✗ missing | 🍌 nano-banana-pro                  | Generate or edit images via Gemini 3 Pro      | openclaw-bundled   |\n|           |                                     | Image (Nano Banana Pro).                      |                    |\n| ✗ missing | 📄 nano-pdf                         | Edit PDFs with natural-language instructions  | openclaw-bundled   |\n|           |                                     | using the nano-pdf CLI.                       |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 node-connect                     | Diagnose OpenClaw node connection and         | openclaw-bundled   |\n|           |                                     | pairing failures for Android, iOS, and macOS  |                    |\n|           |                                     | companion apps. Use when QR/setup code/       |                    |\n|           |                                     | manual connect fails, local Wi-Fi works but   |                    |\n|           |                                     | VPS/tailnet does not, or errors mention       |                    |\n|           |                                     | pairing required, unauthorized, bootstrap     |                    |\n|           |                                     | token invalid or expired, gateway.bind,       |                    |\n|           |                                     | gateway.remote.url, Tailscale, or plugins.    |     