ines, and WolframAlpha knowledge   |                    |\n|           |                                     | queries. No API keys required.                |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 news-summary                     | This skill should be used when the user asks  | openclaw-workspace |\n|           |                                     | for news updates, daily briefings, or what's  |                    |\n|           |                                     | happening in the world. Fetches news from     |                    |\n|           |                                     | trusted international RSS feeds and can       |                    |\n|           |                                     | create voice summaries.                       |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 Proactivity (Proactive Agent)    | Anticipates needs, keeps work moving, and     | openclaw-workspace |\n|           |                                     | improves through use so the agent gets more   |                    |\n|           |                                     | proactive over time.                          |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 Self-Improving + Proactive Agent | Self-reflection + Self-criticism + Self-      | openclaw-workspace |\n|           |                                     | learning + Self-organizing memory. Agent      |                    |\n|           |                                     | evaluates its own work, catches mistakes,     |                    |\n|           |                                     | and improves permanently. Use when (1) a      |                    |\n|           |                                     | command, tool, API, or operation fails; (2)   |                    |\n|           |                                     | the user corrects you or rejects your work;   |                    |\n|           |                                     | (3) you realize your knowledge is outdated    |               