         | Enable and configure Moltbot/Clawdbot memory  | openclaw-workspace |\n|           |                                     | search for persistent context. Use when       |                    |\n|           |                                     | setting up memory, fixing \"goldfish brain,\"   |                    |\n|           |                                     | or helping users configure memorySearch in    |                    |\n|           |                                     | their config. Covers MEMORY.md, daily logs,   |                    |\n|           |                                     | and vector search setup.                      |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 context-manager                  | Auto context management with seamless         | openclaw-workspace |\n|           |                                     | session switching. Monitors usage, triggers   |                    |\n|           |                                     | at 85% threshold, automatically creates new   |                    |\n|           |                                     | session with loaded memory. Zero user         |                    |\n|           |                                     | intervention required. Trigger on \"context\",  |                    |\n|           |                                     | \"memory\", \"session management\", \"context      |                    |\n|           |                                     | limit\", \"memory transfer\".                    |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 multi-search-engine              | Multi search engine integration with 17       | openclaw-workspace |\n|           |                                     | engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced  |                    |\n|           |                                     | search operators, time filters, site search,  |                    |\n|           |                                     | privacy engines, and Wolfra